Properties.Name: activityadditionalparams
Properties.Description: Additional information provided by the external application as JSON. For internal use only.

Properties.Name: activityid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the activity.

Properties.Name: activitytypecode
Properties.Description: Type of activity.

Properties.Name: actualdurationminutes
Properties.Description: Actual duration of the activity in minutes.

Properties.Name: actualend
Properties.Description: Actual end time of the activity.

Properties.Name: actualstart
Properties.Description: Actual start time of the activity.

Properties.Name: allparties
Properties.Description: All activity parties associated with this activity.

Properties.Name: community
Properties.Description: Shows how contact about the social activity originated, such as from Twitter or Facebook. This field is read-only.

Properties.Name: createdby
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the user who created the activity.

Properties.Name: createdon
Properties.Description: Date and time when the activity was created.

Properties.Name: createdonbehalfby
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the delegate user who created the activitypointer.

Properties.Name: deliverylastattemptedon
Properties.Description: Date and time when the delivery of the activity was last attempted.

Properties.Name: deliveryprioritycode
Properties.Description: Priority of delivery of the activity to the email server.

Properties.Name: description
Properties.Description: Description of the activity.

Properties.Name: descriptionblobid
Properties.Description: File that contains description content.

Properties.Name: exchangeitemid
Properties.Description: The message id of activity which is returned from Exchange Server.

Properties.Name: exchangerate
Properties.Description: Exchange rate for the currency associated with the activitypointer with respect to the base currency.

Properties.Name: exchangeweblink
Properties.Description: Shows the web link of Activity of type email.

Properties.Name: instancetypecode
Properties.Description: Type of instance of a recurring series.

Properties.Name: isbilled
Properties.Description: Information regarding whether the activity was billed as part of resolving a case.

Properties.Name: ismapiprivate
Properties.Description: For internal use only.

Properties.Name: isregularactivity
Properties.Description: Information regarding whether the activity is a regular activity type or event type.

Properties.Name: isworkflowcreated
Properties.Description: Information regarding whether the activity was created from a workflow rule.

Properties.Name: lastonholdtime
Properties.Description: Contains the date and time stamp of the last on hold time.

Properties.Name: leftvoicemail
Properties.Description: Left the voice mail

Properties.Name: modifiedby
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of user who last modified the activity.

Properties.Name: modifiedon
Properties.Description: Date and time when activity was last modified.

Properties.Name: modifiedonbehalfby
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the delegate user who last modified the activitypointer.

Properties.Name: onholdtime
Properties.Description: Shows how long, in minutes, that the record was on hold.

Properties.Name: ownerid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the user or team who owns the activity.

Properties.Name: owningbusinessunit
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the business unit that owns the activity.

Properties.Name: owningteam
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the team that owns the activity.

Properties.Name: owninguser
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the user that owns the activity.

Properties.Name: postponeactivityprocessinguntil
Properties.Description: For internal use only.

Properties.Name: prioritycode
Properties.Description: Priority of the activity.

Properties.Name: processid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the Process.

Properties.Name: regardingobjectid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the object with which the activity is associated.

Properties.Name: scheduleddurationminutes
Properties.Description: Scheduled duration of the activity, specified in minutes.

Properties.Name: scheduledend
Properties.Description: Scheduled end time of the activity.

Properties.Name: scheduledstart
Properties.Description: Scheduled start time of the activity.

Properties.Name: sendermailboxid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the mailbox associated with the sender of the email message.

Properties.Name: senton
Properties.Description: Date and time when the activity was sent.

Properties.Name: seriesid
Properties.Description: Uniqueidentifier specifying the id of recurring series of an instance.

Properties.Name: serviceid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of an associated service.

Properties.Name: slaid
Properties.Description: Choose the service level agreement (SLA) that you want to apply to the case record.

Properties.Name: slainvokedid
Properties.Description: Last SLA that was applied to this case. This field is for internal use only.

Properties.Name: sortdate
Properties.Description: Shows the date and time by which the activities are sorted.

Properties.Name: stageid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the Stage.

Properties.Name: statecode
Properties.Description: Status of the activity.

Properties.Name: statuscode
Properties.Description: Reason for the status of the activity.

Properties.Name: subject
Properties.Description: Subject associated with the activity.

Properties.Name: timezoneruleversionnumber
Properties.Description: For internal use only.

Properties.Name: transactioncurrencyid
Properties.Description: Unique identifier of the currency associated with the activitypointer.

Properties.Name: traversedpath
Properties.Description: For internal use only.

Properties.Name: utcconversiontimezonecode
Properties.Description: Time zone code that was in use when the record was created.

Properties.Name: versionnumber
Properties.Description: Version number of the activity.
